These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, epic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | juice   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | adventure   |
| Sport         | rugby | cricket |
| Transport     | ship | van    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, pepper
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, mystery
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, car
1. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the car##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | kiwi     | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | epic  |
| Pet           | goldfish         | rabbit     |
| Transport     | skateboard   | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
