The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, coach
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the coach##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the coach##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | 7up |
| Job         | coach | videographer    |
| Pet         | bird         | rat        |
| Transport   | quad-bike         | boat    |

