1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | mirinda |
| Food          | lettuce   | onion  |
| Hobby         | dancing | chess     |
| Music-Genre   | house  | hip-hop         |

