There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, german
2 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the german is on the far left or far right##3
3. the journalist is the chinese##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | journalist | accountant    |
| Nationality   | chinese       | german |
| Pet           | goat         | goldfish    |
| Sport         | swimming    | biathlon   |

